              Monitor your fitness journey with detailed progress reports and
              analytics.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
      <p>
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Health & Fitness. All rights
        reserved.
      </p>
      <p>
        Follow us on <a href="#">Twitter</a> | <a href="#">Facebook</a> |
        <a href="#">Instagram</a>
      </p>
    </footer>
